                    <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
                        <strong>ASHRAE 62.1</strong> classifies Garbage Rooms as "Air Class 3," typically mandating 100% exhaust. However, we utilize the <strong>IAQ Procedure (Section 6.3)</strong>.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
                        By cleaning the air and validating via mass-balance analysis, we <strong>redesignate</strong> the air to "Class 2" (Section 5.13). This legally removes the requirement for a dedicated vertical shaft.
                    </p>
                    <div class="border border-slate-700 rounded-lg p-4 bg-slate-800/50">
